summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the condemnation proceedings to acquire land and other property necessary for the laying off, opening, widening and establishing of 5th Avenue North between Valley Street and Republican Street under Ordinance 100337, King County Cause No. 741003, accepting a condemnation award (Parcel 4) in connection therewith and making a reimbursable appropriation from the Arterial City Street Fund therefor.
